{"tid":163821,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好懷念十二歲前的日子","createTime":"2017-03-20T09:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T10:57:22.000Z","uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe5ce546b833bc342304a45aecabe2caa31c2389","tid":163821,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:17:26.000Z","msg":"其實應該因為青春期<br />\n生理分泌亂晒所以係咁亂諗野<br />\n到最後爆被醫畜話有精神病<br />\n<br />\n17歲個年因某些原因trigger到出現左一個好痴線的想法<br />\n講出黎俾大家恥笑下啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中五某日在家上網<br />\n突然間有個想法深信自己細個被性侵犯過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（當然我從來冇）<br />\n<br />\n直頭發惡夢果陣有把女聲咁樣同我講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是所謂症狀更加嚴重 好似越黎越痴線<br />\n<br />\n之後斷斷續績食下藥<br />\n呢個delusion false belief一直浮浮沉沉<br />\n<br />\n當然而家我知真係因為diseased brain先會有此想法<br />\n<br />\n但阻止唔到我對家人有戒心<br />\n好驚有日會傷害佢地<br />\n<br />\n不過今年的我清楚意識到12歲前的感覺與日子永遠回不來。<br />\n<br />\nbtw 識英文可自己睇下外國呢篇文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ipt-forensics.com/journal/volume7/j7_3_5.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipt-forensics.com%2Fjournal%2Fvolume7%2Fj7_3_5.htm&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=bf2a6a83\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ipt-forensics.com/journal/volume7/j7_3_5.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n係外國醫生將paranoid schiz patients 的妄想誤診成Childhood sexual abuse induced PTSD"},{"pid":"0cfe33ce429894ae431d6e19cfa14337abb0760d","tid":163821,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:18:20.000Z","msg":"我的生命簡直是一文不值"},{"pid":"b6e5bec4b773cdb92fec840d990d28fc7c577f5a","tid":163821,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:19:08.000Z","msg":"上次有人問點解我睇得明d英文<br />\n<br />\n講真普通少少英文仲睇得明既"},{"pid":"2e5e1ed1f90b18689b8d151897f535cf0653f83c","tid":163821,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:21:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次有人問點解我睇得明d英文<br />\n<br />\n講真普通少少英文仲睇得明既</blockquote><br />\n雖然本垃圾讀唔成書"},{"pid":"fd8032eafe85841757c6ca636fbfab4ec7399b6a","tid":163821,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:22:36.000Z","msg":"聽聞有d病人發癲妄想自己個女被女醫生性侵犯。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669e8cfeea7bb97f297066db2990b55839c0d822","tid":163821,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:30:31.000Z","msg":"灰到核爆"},{"pid":"59bf42e003d1915338d94f2fa8d93a9536cd76b0","tid":163821,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07ff2de7abb2882af2775753a2844c2e351bce6","tid":163821,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:48:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得自己的身份很差"},{"pid":"b2160e578c048bc11961cfb18a365e3012fed65b","tid":163821,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:48:02.000Z","msg":"我想重新開始"},{"pid":"a88ad6e41018e57927ffe379790bb3126ce44313","tid":163821,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:57:22.000Z","msg":"又不想話俾醫畜聽"}]}